(314, 74, 'description', 'The system can monitor prescription (POM), and control measures to ensure that Narcotic, Controlled, and semi-controlled are not available to the layman. it aims also to:\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n 	<li><span lang=\"en\">Achieve integrated governance of the process of prescribing and dispensing all medicines that are only dispensed under a prescription from a licensed doctor.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span lang=\"en\">Add the list of prescription medications (POM) to a working system.</span></li>\r\n 	<li>Make Narcotic, Controlled, and semi-controlled available only for medical use.</li>\r\n 	<li>Prevent their diversion into illicit channels.</li>\r\n 	<li>EliminatePrescription Medicine (POM)trafficking and misuse.</li>\r\n 	<li>Patient Monitoring (the system can monitor patient medication usage to identify potential misuse or overuse).</li>\r\n 	<li>Alerting system if there are issues like misuse or potential addiction.</li>\r\n 	<li>Reporting: the system can generate reports on medication prescriptions, medication usage, and any violation.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
