(831, 141, 'entry_content_0_description', 'Mission of the National Platform for Controlled Medication:The<a href=\"https://www.whitehouse.gov/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/National-Drug-Control-2022Strategy.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-auth=\"NotApplicable\" data-linkindex=\"4\"><em>Portal</em></a>focuses on the following critical drivers:\r\n<ol start=\"1\" type=\"1\">\r\n 	<li>Achieving integrated governance of the process of prescribing and dispensing human medication that is dispensed only by prescription (POM) (narcotics, controlled medication, and semi-controlled medication), from authorized licensed doctors it is starting from importing and storing it in warehouses and distributing it to the pharmacies and dispensing it to the inpatients and outpatients in all UAE.<b><i><u></u></i></b></li>\r\n 	<li>Achieving integrated governance of the process of prescribing and dispensing veterinary medication so they reach the beneficiaries through the health and medical system in force in the country, with specific procedures and the process and technologies to be implemented.<b><i><u></u></i></b></li>\r\n 	<li>Achieving integrated governance of the process ofAnti-doping program seek to<strong></strong><strong>maintain the integrity of sports in terms of respect for rules, other competitors, fair competition, a level playing field, and the value of clean sport to the world</strong><b>.</b>To achieve this goal, anti-doping programs rely on rules, education/prevention, disclosure and notification, testing, and getting to know those who break the rules.<b><i><u></u></i></b></li>\r\n 	<li>It instructs competent bodies to prioritize actions that will get the safe prescribing, dispensing, correct use, and high-quality care they need and make better use of data to guide all these efforts to the ideal method of use.<i><u></u></i></li>\r\n 	<li><span lang=\"en\">which aims to govern the field of controlled, semi-controlled, and narcotic medication and vet medication and anti-doping, and inventory tracking for control and semi-control and narcotic from the importing the medication officially from outlets of the state, transporting, storing, and distributing them in the country, knowing the size of the description, expense, and inventory at the outlets.</span></li>\r\n</ol>'),
