(1156, 175, 'paragraphs_0_description', '<span lang=\"en\">The Ministry of Interior project owner, MOI has considered one of the best government agencies within the United Arab Emirates in terms of the quality of digital services it provides to all components of the UAE society, as it recently won several awards and is the best government entity in digital services, and the Ministry of Interior aspires to continuous improvement and to achieve strategic goals permanently.Accordingly, the Ministry of Interior launched the \"National Platform for Controlled Medication \", in collaboration and coordination with the stick holder all health authorities Ministry of Health and Prevention (MOHP), the</span><span lang=\"en-US\">Ministry of climate change and Environment (MOCCE), the Department of Health Abu Dhabi (DOH), Dubai Health Authority (DHA), Emirates Health Services (EHS), Federal Authority for identity citizenship, customs, port Security (ICA) and the private Health sector.</span>'),
(1157, 175, '_paragraphs_0_description', 'field_632c3daa6dc3e'),
(1158, 175, 'paragraphs_1_title', 'About Us'),
(1159, 175, '_paragraphs_1_title', 'field_632c3d8f6dc3d'),
(1160, 175, 'paragraphs_1_description', '<span lang=\"en-US\">The<b><i>National Platform for Controlled Medication:</i></b>created by<b><i>Tahaluf Al Emarat Technical Solution LLC</i></b>,</span>is a cutting-edge healthcare support portal whose mission is to pave the way for a healthier and secure future,by tracking the(POM) (narcotics, controlled and semi-controlled medication)from entering the country until they reach the patients hands,thehealth sector has witnessed great qualitative accomplishments in a bid to meet various health challenges inhealthcare servicesand keep pace with global developments.We aim to advance and enhance the quality of healthcare services for the betterment of our society and all of UAE.<span lang=\"en\">Establish an integrated tracking process for the movement of controlled drugs and restricted medicines. Also, for vet medication, and inventory tracking for all controlled medication, to reach to easy and safe use.</span>'),
